Package org.androidtransfuse.intentFactory

Interface Summary
IntentFactory.IntentAdapterFactory Intent factory class used for testing purposes.
IntentFactoryStrategy Strategy class defining a Contract for the given Android Context, specifying the relevant parameters to build an Android Intent.
 

Class Summary
AbstractIntentFactoryStrategy Abstract Base class defining the required parameters to build an Intent.
ActivityIntentFactoryStrategy Activity specific Base class defining how to start an Activity by Intent.
IntentFactory Factory for building an Android Intent from an input IntentStrategy.
ServiceIntentFactoryStrategy Service specific Base class defining how to start an Activity by Intent.
